reviewText: I really love this movie.  Another Cinderella-type movie.  I wish I am going to be able to purchase Au Pair II through Amazon soon.

I Love this movie,,,Ive seen it twice on tv, and have searched for months for all 3 movies, and have had no success, I want these movies so bad, their such good clean family movies, the kids just love them, so please help me to be able to purchase them,,,
Thanks, Sheila R. McIntosh,,Ky.

Please try hard to get this on DVD. I taped it off the TV a few years ago and it is a totally fun movie, but now, my tape is missing....I loaned it out so many times !!
Thanks from Lorraine in New Zealand
